  Remove intermediate version.

*xtrs-4.9d-r3 (13 Apr 2014)

  13 Apr 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> +xtrs-4.9d-r3.ebuild:
  Binary patch LS-DOS 6.3.1 to patchlevel L, fixing the year 2012 date bug.
  Restrict bindist with USE=ls-dos; permission to redistribute modified files
  has not been granted.

  12 Apr 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> xtrs-4.9d-r1.ebuild,
  xtrs-4.9d-r2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Rename ldos USE flag to ls-dos. Add missing dependency on app-arch/unzip.

*xtrs-4.9d-r2 (31 Jan 2014)

  31 Jan 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> +xtrs-4.9d-r2.ebuild:
  Use upstream default locations to look for ROM and disk files. Update ebuild
  to EAPI 5. Inherit readme.gentoo.eclass.

  30 Nov 2012; Joe Peterson <lavajoe@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove myself as a maintainer

  20 Nov 2012; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> -xtrs-4.9d.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  20 Nov 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xtrs-4.9d-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #441074

  04 Nov 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xtrs-4.9d-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #441074

